{"tid":2312014,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"柏傲莊 II 連錄5宗撻訂　料殺訂逾296萬","createTime":"2020-12-04T13:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T10:53:48.000Z","uid":103315,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a005bd40081a7642da16e687e77fcbb567314b41","tid":2312014,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"新世界發展（0017）與港鐵（0066）旗下的大圍站上蓋柏傲莊II 在上周四（11月26日）第4輪銷售315伙，單日累沽9成單位。不過，根據成交紀錄冊顯示，最新錄5宗撻訂，單位均在第4輪銷售當日成交，料遭發展商沒收5%訂金，合共損失逾296萬元。<br />\n<br />\n是次單位為5A座15樓A室、7A座57樓D室、6B座的17樓F室及19樓E室及60樓C室，面積由324至866平方呎，成交額介乎752.8萬至1,955.6萬元。不過，買家同於簽訂臨約後交易未有進展，料涉及5%訂金，殺訂金額由37.64萬至97.78萬元，即共殺訂296.17萬元。<br />\n<br />\n當中，4位買家採用「180天現金優惠付款計劃」及1位買家採用「建築期付款」。<br />\n<br />\n柏傲莊上月共錄11宗撻訂，殺訂金額由32.6萬至97.87萬元。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/557818/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-ii-%E9%80%A3%E9%8C%845%E5%AE%97%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82-%E6%96%99%E6%AE%BA%E8%A8%82%E9%80%BE296%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F557818%2F%25E6%259F%258F%25E5%2582%25B2%25E8%258E%258A-ii-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E9%258C%25845%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2592%25BB%25E8%25A8%2582-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2580%25BE296%25E8%2590%25AC&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1wxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=2128af25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/557818/%E6%9F%8F%E5%82%B2%E8%8E%8A-ii-%E9%80%A3%E9%8C%845%E5%AE%97%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82-%E6%96%99%E6%AE%BA%E8%A8%82%E9%80%BE296%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"8940905d2148044dad69e2ea9d0c6cce2c198384","tid":2312014,"uid":75686,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"a005bd40081a7642da16e687e77fcbb567314b41","tid":2312014,"uid":103315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:36:48.000Z","msg":"新世界發展（0017）與港鐵（0066）旗下的大圍站上蓋柏傲莊I